ram page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Catch Responsive Pro theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://catchthemes.com/themes/catch-responsive-pro/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/catch.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Catch Responsive Pro is an extremely flexible and customizable WordPress theme suitable for almost any kind of professional website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://catchthemes.com/themes/catch-responsive-pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Catch Responsive theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Throne theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/throne-personal-blogmagazine-wordpress-theme/8134834\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/throne.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Professional WordPress blog/magazine theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/throne-personal-blogmagazine-wordpress-theme/8134834\">Purchase Throne theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Chronicle theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/chronicle-premium-theme/\"><img class=\"align